e
n\to\infty
n'=\frac n2
 \lim_{n\to\infty}(1 + \frac 2n)^n=\lim_{n\to\infty}\left(1 + \frac 1{\frac n2}\right)^{2(\frac n2)}=\lim_{n'\to\infty}\left((1 + \frac 1{n'})^{n'}\right)^2=e^2 
 \lim_{n \to \infty} \left(1 + \frac{2}{n} \right)^n = e^{\lim_{n \to \infty} \frac{\ln \left( 1 + \frac{2}{n} \right) }{\frac{1}{n}}} \overset{\ast}{=} e^{\lim_{n\to\infty } \frac{-\frac{2}{n^2}\frac{1}{1 + 2/n}}{-1/n^2}} = e^{\lim_{n\to \infty} \frac{2}{1+2/n} } = e^2  
